headline: Invesco Canada announces cash distributions for its ETFs
summary: Invesco Canada Ltd. ("Invesco") announced today the November 2024 distributions for its exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Unitholders of record on November 28, 2024, will receive cash distributions payable on December 6, 2024.
